descriptionHtml:
What is USB Vision ?
As we know that digital contents are getting popular now, more & more people fall into thismagnificent world. However, have you ever think about how to protect the valuable content you own ?

How to achieve a great distribution without worrying about piracy ?
With C-Protek Vision, you can get rid of all your worries, but just enjoy the great time in the digital world.

What can C-Protek Vision brings to you?
1. Special secure USB drive: With built-in multiple secure mechanism both in software and hardware, digital content can be
completely protected.
2. Secure source maker: To meet the market strategies and guarantee the consistency of contents, this solution allows publishers to make their own source USB device, and mass production according to their needs (MOQ: 100pcs).
3. Sustained connection with users: C-Protek Vision solution enable publishers to set up the website likage within digital contents. Therefore, users will have a great channel to keep in touch with publishers.
4. A real content protection solution: C-Protek Vision solution enable publishers to set up the website likage within digital contents. Therefore, users will have a great channel to keep in touch with publishers.

Outstanding Features of C-Protek Vision ?
● Safety: Powerful content protection mechanism assure a safe content distribution.
● Saving: More flexible to achieve segmented production, no more heavy stocks.
● Efficiency: Easy to catch the trend of market with least production time.
● Bonus: Printing service makes content stylish and fancy.

Support Formats ?
Digital teaching materials and etc.
Video records, Trailers of movies, Introduction of products and etc.
Audio books, Talking book, audio albums, demos and etc.
E-book, E-papers, Products catalog and etc.

Suitable for ?
Digital industries: e-Book, Video / Music.
Outstanding Features: Internal training, school education, cram school, e-learning.
Enterprise application: Important meeting materials, activities records.
